node.text:
You know Barbie, but have you met… Barbie? 💖 That’s right; Barbie Roberts meets Barbie Roberts, and they have more in common than just their name! The two became fast friends and chose nicknames inspired by their hometowns – Malibu and Brooklyn – to better differentiate when they’re together.
 
Gather your kids and join the two friends in this dorm room unboxing to get to know #Barbie “Brooklyn” Roberts!

It’s the sound of the summer, and the musical adventure of a lifetime! 👑🎶

Listen to the #Barbie Princess Adventure original soundtrack NOW on @AppleMusic, @Spotify and @Pandora, before the film comes to Netflix on Tuesday.

node.text: Pony up for a summer of styling fun and animal friendship! 🐴 From color reveal highlights and hair clip accessories, kids can saddle up for the mane attraction no matter where the summer takes them with #Barbie.

node.accessibility_caption: Barbie stands next to her horse. Both have colorful stripes and clips in their hair
Barbie sits on her horse while a pony stands next to them. All of them have colorful clips in their hair.
Barbie stands next to her horse and pony outside of the stable.
The gymnast doll holds two hoops.

node.text: It’s all about finding your balance 🤸 and jumping through hoops to achieve your dreams! 🏅 #Barbie #YouCanBeAnything

node.accessibility_caption: The gymnast doll holds two hoops.
The gymnast doll stands in front of the bar with all of her accessories scattered around.
The gymnast doll is dressed in her warmup suit.
The gymnast doll holds two batons.
A toy box filled with a group of diverse dolls.

node.text: When we #MixUpTheToyBox with dolls featuring a range of skin tones, body types, and disabilities, we help kids understand and celebrate the importance of representation.

node.accessibility_caption: The three new color reveal dolls stand together in front of a pool filled with bubbles and foam.

node.text: Get that summer feeling bubbling with #Barbie Color Reveal! The Foam series comes with all-new surprises, from fruit-scented foam, kinetic sand, and even a kid-sized charm bracelet for the little ones. ☀️🍉🍍🍓 Shop now at @walmart

Gather your kids and join the two friends in this dorm room unboxing to get to know #Barbie “Brooklyn” Roberts!
